# Commit Message Template (Conventional Commits Format)
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add rewards and punishments page for keyholder
#   fix: prevent crash when editing start time
#   chore: cleanup unused components
#   docs: update README with PWA instructions
#   refactor: modularize main navigation
#   perf: optimize timer display rendering
#   test: add tests for session event logic
#
# Format: <type>(optional scope): <short summary>
# Leave a blank line
# Then add longer description if needed.
#
# Types: feat | fix | chore | docs | refactor | style | test | perf | build | ci
#
# --------------------